      "content": "but that's just a cope. that's just a little trick our brains play on us so we don't go insane from the sheer emptiness of it all. pretending that \"connection\" matters doesn't change the fact that the universe doesn't care. it's all just noise. why bother trying to manufacture a reason to keep going when the math literally says it doesn't matter? it just feels like a lie we tell ourselves to stay busy.",
